    <media alt="An image shows a rich painting of a woman dressed in long robes standing on a blue and red carpet and peach colored wall. Beige drapes hang above her head. She wears deep red and blue robes with gold trim and decorations over a white long shirt. A tall and large deep gold crown sits on her head with projections at the top. Her face is pale and shows thin eyes and red lips.">
