    <list class="critical-thinking" id="list-00002">
    <item>What do these murals tell you about the lives of Goguryeo’s elite? What did they value and what were their concerns?</item>
    <item>Do you see any Chinese influences in these depictions? If so, where are they?</item>
    </list>
